  <scopecontent id="aspace_ref48">
    <head>Scope and Contents</head>
<p>This small collection documents graduating classes at various public and private schools in Brooklyn. Additionally, there are two photographs of the staff of Boys High School's student publication, the <emph render="italic">Recorder</emph>. Some photographs list student names on the verso, but most do not.</p>  </scopecontent>
